        </aside>
        <div class="lm-article__body">
          <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">From idea to inbox in seven days.</h3>

          <div class="lm-checklist__group">
            <h4>Day 1 — Beat &amp; hunt</h4>
            <ul class="lm-checklist">
              <li>Chosen the beat (one beat, not three).</li>
              <li>Made a list of 8–10 outlets, 15–25 specific reporters.</li>
              <li>Read 2–3 recent pieces from each reporter.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="lm-checklist__group">
            <h4>Day 2 — Data</h4>
            <ul class="lm-checklist">
              <li>Identified dataset A and dataset B (both public, both on the beat).</li>
              <li>Googled the combination. Confirmed no one has multiplied them publicly.</li>
              <li>Pulled both datasets, archived a copy with date stamp.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="lm-checklist__group">
            <h4>Day 3 — Compute</h4>
            <ul class="lm-checklist">
              <li>Produced one headline number.</li>
              <li>Produced a local cut (top 50 metros, or by state, or by industry).</li>
              <li>Drafted the two-page methodology document.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="lm-checklist__group">
            <h4>Day 4 — Write</h4>
            <ul class="lm-checklist">
              <li>Wrote the headline. Showed it to one person who isn't in your business.</li>
              <li>Built the one-page brief.</li>
              <li>Cleaned the CSV / sheet for sharing.</li>
              <li>Built one publication-ready chart.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="lm-checklist__group">
            <h4>Day 5 — Pitch</h4>
            <ul class="lm-checklist">
              <li>Wrote 5 personalized Wave 1 pitches.</li>
              <li>Verified all 5 email addresses.</li>
              <li>Sent Wave 1, Tuesday 7–10am their time.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="lm-checklist__group">
            <h4>Day 6 — Wait</h4>
            <ul class="lm-checklist">
              <li>Did not pester. Did not refresh. Did the next thing on your list.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="lm-checklist__group">
            <h4>Day 7 — Wave 2</h4>
            <ul class="lm-checklist">
              <li>Wrote 10–15 Wave 2 pitches.</li>
              <li>Sent Wave 2, Thursday morning.</li>
              <li>Logged everything in the tracker.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <h3>Templates.</h3>

          <h4>The one-page brief</h4>
          <pre class="lm-template"><strong>[HEADLINE — &lt;9 WORDS]</strong>

The finding: [One sentence with the number.]

Three takeaways:
  — [Bullet, one sentence]
  — [Bullet, one sentence]
  — [Bullet, one sentence]

Data sources: [Dataset A, year/version] · [Dataset B, year/version]
