own way. Happy to hold it under embargo until [date], or set up 15 minutes with the
analyst who built it.

— [Your name]
[Title], [Company] · [Phone]</pre>

          <h4>The follow-up</h4>
          <pre class="lm-template"><strong>Subject:</strong> Re: [original subject]

Hi [First name],

